      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DANGEROUS (7) is back from a spell of three-and-a-half months and looks to be right up to the mark following a recent trial win. Beat grand pacer Bulletproof Boy when scoring two back at Melton and generally comes to hand very quickly with four wins from seven first-up appearances. Has to contend with a wide draw but is well-placed to take this out. JILLIBY WILLOW (8) backs up after tackling some strong opposition on Saturday at Melton. Owns good statistics both here and at the distance and there is no harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. WESTERN SONADOR (6) has been freshened but was kept up to the mark with two trial placings. ABOUTTIME (4) has had a year off but flies fresh winning four of six attempts and was readied with a trial win. Strikes at 50 per cent here so watch the betting.",
